STATE
v.
HITCHCOCK. 2018-0012 Supreme Court of Ohio. February 28, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

On review of an order certifying a conflict. The court determines that a conflict exists. Cause accepted and held for decision in 2016-1848, State v. Paige, and briefing schedule stayed.

DeGenaro, J., not participating.
